13:01.566 --> 13:03.600
Thank you so much
for recommending me.

13:03.600 --> 13:05.133
Judith: Oh, you're working
for Kellar Andrews?

13:05.133 --> 13:06.400
I used to be there.

13:06.400 --> 13:07.433
Woman 2:
Oh, really?

13:07.433 --> 13:08.566
Where are you now?

13:08.566 --> 13:10.466
Insomnia and droolstein.

13:11.500 --> 13:14.300
It's a... it was a joke.

13:14.300 --> 13:15.433
I'm on mat leave.

13:15.433 --> 13:16.600
Oh, great.

13:16.600 --> 13:17.533
Great.

13:19.366 --> 13:21.700
So, uh, how are things
with the Stohn action?

13:21.700 --> 13:23.633
Oh, they settled that
about two months ago.

13:23.633 --> 13:25.266
Do you know about
the Crosby lawsuit?

13:25.266 --> 13:26.633
Crosby?
Doesn't ring a bell.

13:26.633 --> 13:30.633
Really?
It's all over the news.

13:30.633 --> 13:34.500
Oh, well, maybe I should pick
up a paper once in a while.

13:34.500 --> 13:36.100
Then find time to read it.

13:36.100 --> 13:38.033
(polite laughter)

13:39.533 --> 13:41.533
I thought your firm
won Crosby at trial.

13:41.533 --> 13:44.333
Woman 2: We did, but then
we lost on the appeal.

13:44.333 --> 13:45.666
Who was the judge
on that?

13:45.666 --> 13:47.100
Ugh, Kelly,
he was so difficult.

13:47.100 --> 13:48.000
I know, surprising.

13:48.000 --> 13:49.266
Excuse me.

13:49.266 --> 13:50.533
I thought you would've
really--

13:50.533 --> 13:52.500
(makes playful sounds)

13:52.500 --> 13:53.666
(telephone rings)

13:55.300 --> 13:56.266
Oh.

13:57.433 --> 13:59.633
Hello, Judith,
everything is fine.

13:59.633 --> 14:01.266
Oh, thank you.

14:01.266 --> 14:03.300
That is such a relief,
I cannot tell you.

14:03.300 --> 14:05.133
So are you rocking it out?

14:05.133 --> 14:07.000
Oh, yeah, you know it.

14:07.000 --> 14:09.266
(Erica chuckles,
Max coos)

14:09.266 --> 14:10.333
Is that Max?

14:10.333 --> 14:11.466
Erica: Uh, yeah,
everything's fine.

14:11.466 --> 14:13.500
He just needed a little
more tiring out.

14:13.500 --> 14:15.000
It's almost eight, Erica.

14:15.000 --> 14:17.366
I told you to put him
to bed at seven.

14:17.366 --> 14:19.333
I know, Jude,
but he was crying.

14:19.333 --> 14:22.533
Of course he was crying,
he's a baby.

14:22.533 --> 14:24.666
Why is it always, always
so hard for you

14:24.666 --> 14:26.166
