All right, just hang on.

22:32.333 --> 22:33.333
I...

22:33.333 --> 22:34.533
(breathes deeply)

22:34.533 --> 22:36.133
I promised myself that
I wasn't gonna cancel.

22:36.133 --> 22:38.033
So, max and I are
coming with you.

22:38.033 --> 22:38.700
And that's that!

22:38.700 --> 22:40.200
Couldn't we just
leave him here

22:40.200 --> 22:41.700
and put him to bed?

22:41.700 --> 22:43.733
I mean, I'm sure Ethan
wouldn't mind if he's...

22:43.733 --> 22:46.033
Well, I'm not sure
I feel totally comfortable

22:46.033 --> 22:47.266
