some stranger's baby.

22:47.266 --> 22:49.566
Yeah. you know, and Ethan's
gotta help me drink

22:49.566 --> 22:51.700
four garbage cans full
of purple jesus', so...

22:51.700 --> 22:54.300
It's Michael's room buddy's
annual house party.

22:54.300 --> 22:55.300
See ya.

22:55.300 --> 22:56.566
Erica:
Have fun.

22:56.566 --> 22:58.600
Look, Jude,
it's gonna be fine.

22:58.600 --> 23:00.700
He's just gonna sleep
over my shoulder.

23:00.700 --> 23:02.633
We're gonna have
a great time.

23:02.633 --> 23:04.300
Hey, you need me.

23:06.666 --> 23:09.733
I guess.

23:09.733 --> 23:12.733
We're froshin',
we're froshin'.

23:12.733 --> 23:15.466
