and he's tired.

24:06.700 --> 24:09.666
I have to take him to bed.
Jude, I'm so sorry.

24:09.666 --> 24:11.733
Look, was it my idea
to be frosh leaders?

24:11.733 --> 24:13.533
No, okay,
I did this for you.

24:13.533 --> 24:14.533
And despite that,

24:14.533 --> 24:16.766
I held the bag all day
at the carwash, okay.

24:16.766 --> 24:19.033
This, I told you
this is so stupid!

24:19.033 --> 24:20.633
I know, and I'm sorry,
but I...

24:20.633 --> 24:23.400
I mean, how was I supposed
to leave him at home?

24:23.400 --> 24:24.633
You could've gotten
a baby-sitter.

24:24.633 --> 24:25.633
I am the baby-sitter!

24:25.633 --> 24:28.033
Just take him home
to his mom, okay?

24:28.033 --> 24:30.333
Here, take her some condoms
